    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car has been my baby since day one\u2014always kept in the garage, meticulously cleaned, and it still feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. It is in truly pristine shape with no flaws to speak of. If you're looking for a ride that\u2019s been loved and kept in tip-top condition, you\u2019ve found it! I\u2019m so excited for someone else to get behind the wheel and enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
