    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This 997.2 Carrera S is a definitive example of naturally aspirated precision, powered by a 3.8L Direct Fuel Injection (DFI) flat-six that delivers linear power across the entire rev range. The chassis is equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a limited-slip differential, ensuring exceptional lateral grip and corner-exit stability. Every mechanical component, from the 7-speed PDK dual-clutch transmission to the ventilated cross-drilled rotors, has been maintained to an exacting standard. The factory paint remains in showroom condition with zero evidence of road rash or oxidation, while the cabin's bolsters and tactile interfaces show no wear. A mechanically peerless specimen for the collector who demands an uncompromised driving experience.",
      "price": 49500.0,
