      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 Are you ready to drive your dream car? I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, it is in truly stunning shape! It looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014not a single speck out of place. It\u2019s been loved and pampered since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you're looking for something that feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you! Come say hi and take it for a spin!",
