    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a definitive AP2-generation Honda S2000, showcasing the pinnacle of high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. This example features the F22C1 longitudinal inline-four, characterized by its high-compression ratio and seamless VTEC engagement. The drivetrain is anchored by a legendary 6-speed close-ratio manual gearbox and a Torsen limited-slip differential, ensuring precise power delivery to the rear wheels. The chassis remains structurally flawless, utilizing the rigid X-bone frame and a sophisticated four-wheel independent double-wishbone suspension geometry for unparalleled lateral stability. Maintenance has been meticulously performed with a focus on mechanical longevity, including verified valve clearances and fluid analysis. This is a collector-grade, unmodified specimen that retains its factory-engineered balance and tactile feedback.",
